title: My collection of House, Electro house, Dubstep, Drum&Bass, H
description:
This is my current collection of songs from the EDM genres such as House, electro house, progressive house, dubstep, drum&bass, hardstyle, some moombahton and trance. The mp3 quality varies from 128 to 320 kbps. The ones from the last year are almost all 320kbps. If you like it, please leave a comment and share for a time!

I tried to put a full list of titles here but it was way too long.
